  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "Hera Arms CQR手枪式握把一体化枪托",
      "en": "AR-15 Hera Arms CQR pistol grip/buttstock"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "HA CQR",
      "en": "CQR AR15"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "这种枪托是为民用市场设计的，也可用于执法和军事用途。以广泛使用的AR15平台为基础，制造出一种最坚固、紧凑的步枪系统。CQR步枪枪托可以很简单地替换使用军规卡宾枪缓冲管的AR-15步枪枪托。",
      "en": "Designed for the cilvilian market as well as for military use, to create one of the most rigid and compact Rifle Systems based on the widely available AR-15 platform. The CQR Riflestock is an easy to install replacement buttstock for Mil-Spec AR-15 Rifles using a Mil-Spec Carbine buffer tube."
    },
